        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "DATes: The purpose of this notice is to allow an additional 3o days for public comments. Comments are encouraged and will be accepted until November 29, 2012. This process is conducted in accordance with 5 CFR 1320.10.",
        "bbox": [
