        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "(4) Minimize the burden of the collection of information on those who are to respond, including through the use of appropriate automated, electronic, mechanical, or other technological collection techniques or other forms of information technology, e.g., permitting electronic submission of responses.",
        "bbox": [
